<subSubSection pageId="169" pageNumber="447" type="conservation">
<paragraph blockId="169.[1401,2608,296,845]" pageId="169" pageNumber="447">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[1403,1752,655,684]" pageId="169" pageNumber="447">Status and Conservation.</emphasis>
Classified as Least Concern on The IUCN Red List. The Trinidad Water Rat presumably has a large overall population and is tolerant of some habitat disturbance.
</paragraph>
